        <item>
            <title>【評測】Sky X Studio《忍者戰士飛影》，武裝豐富 + 大比例 + 高可動性</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/07/sky-x-studiotobikage/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sky-x-studiotobikage</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/07/sky-x-studiotobikage/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 03:56:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1279785</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>愈來愈多廠方推出懷舊機械人動畫的超合金 Figure，真的太好了，今次要開箱的是 39 年前的機械人動畫《忍者戰士飛影》中的飛影，但想不到一向都細細隻的飛影，今次廠方會用大比例製作，實物是這麼的大隻。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC6501" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54188218504/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54188218504_feb53529fb_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6501" width="1024" height="618" /></a>▲可見飛影都真係幾大隻</p><p>1985 年的《忍者戰士飛影》，不知大家還記不記得呢，作為一部無人駕駛的機械人 (前期)，有超強的戰力，總會在主角們不夠打時就會出場助陣 (出場時就會播放飛影專用 BGM)，好像開無雙那樣，戰局就會逆轉；還記得當年每集最期待的就是與黑獅子、鳳雷鷹、爆龍其中之一合體，爆龍的大絕最有霸氣。不過後期由阿祖駕駛飛影後，感覺像是被弱化了似的&#8230;&#8230;</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_48858"  width="590" height="443"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="443" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vLse-ehXuis?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_94049"  width="590" height="443"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="443" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MNx5FP_nZx0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>《忍者戰士飛影》亦有在好幾部機戰作品登場，《機戰 UX》，《機戰 Impact》中都可説是主力的機體 (後期由阿祖駕駛後)，遊戲前期階段，不可操縱的飛影可説是經驗值+金錢的小偷，小編對它又愛又恨。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279797" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《機戰 UX》的飛影</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《機戰 UX》飛影的必殺分身攻擊</p><h2>塗裝細膩質感十足</h2><p>説了那麼多回憶後，要説回正題了，香港廠方 Sky X Studio 推出的《忍者戰士飛影》合金 Figure，作品不但忠實還原了動畫中的經典形象，更在機體的細節、可動性以及豐富的武裝方面，作出了很出色的表現。飛影整體色調飽和度高，有強烈的金屬質感，細節部分也處理得非常細膩，例如身上的紋路都清晰可見，而眼睛部分本身已是作金色塗裝，亦有 LED 發光效果，雙眼的黃光是非常的光亮的，著燈後非常有神。除了關節部份外，飛影部分部件也採用了合金材質，增加重量手感也提升了耐用性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279804" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6212-528x580.jpg" alt="" width="528" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6212-528x580.jpg 528w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6212-scaled.jpg 819w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 528px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲很有型的包裝盒</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6219-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6219-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6219-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全綵印刷説明書</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279805" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6218-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6218-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6218-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲説明書主要是講解武器的裝設情況</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279807" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6220-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6220-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6220-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲開箱後的主體板件</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279808" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6361-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6361-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6361-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另一板的武器配件</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279812" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6234-694x443.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="443" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6234-694x443.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6234-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲頭蓋採用磁吸，LED 燈入電位情況</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC6377" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54188217649/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54188217649_bb8b228cf1_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6377" width="1024" height="930" /></a> ▲眼睛的 LED 燈效是非常光，很有神。</p><p><a title="_DSC6227" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54188376735/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54188376735_d433574733_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6227" width="673" height="1024" /></a><br /><a title="_DSC6229" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54187933921/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54187933921_262797001d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6229" width="721" height="1024" /></a></p><h2>可動性高造型掌豐富</h2><p>飛影的可動性就有如動畫一樣，都是非常高可動靈活，它雖然大大隻，實際上肢體可擺出很多動作，全身各處關節均採用了球形關節設計，確保了各個部位的靈活度。肩部、肘部、手腕等部位的可動範圍較大，可以擺出各種動態姿勢，腰部關節的設計也非常巧妙，能夠實現大幅度的彎曲，讓飛影的動作更加靈活。特別值得一提的是，小腿部分設計有連動裝甲，當小腿彎曲時，裝甲會隨之開合，增加動態效果及細節；提供的造型手掌也非常豐富，大大提高了飛影的可玩性。值得一提的是頭部的忍者帽末端是採用銀色軟膠製作，方便頭部作任何方位的擺動時都不會受到阻礙，這個貼心的設計相當不錯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279809" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6230-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6230-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6230-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲忍者帽末端是用軟膠製，頭部如何擺動都不會有阻礙</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279811" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6233-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6233-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6233-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲頭部可以 360 度轉動</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279813" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6494-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6494-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6494-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲大腿的連動式關節，會見到內藏機械結構，以及可動情況</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279814" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6495-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6495-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6495-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲手臂的可動性情況</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279818" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6500-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6500-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6500-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲肩膊關節可拉出，提升可動性</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279815" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6496-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6496-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6496-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲前後裙甲可拉起，方便大腿作出大幅度動作</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279816" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6497-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6497-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6497-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲腰部的可動性</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279817" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6498-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6498-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6498-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> ▲腰部的可動性</p><p><a title="_DSC6375" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54188201663/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54188201663_d2fe57750c_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6375" width="642" height="1024" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲平衡度不錯，擺出這樣的 Pose 也不需用支架</p><h2>超豐富的武器配件</h2><p>飛影配備了多種武器配件，忍者刀、手裡劍、星形光線炮、十字弩都有，充分還原了動畫中飛影武器的多樣性，而武器配件的細節刻畫也非常精緻，提升了整體質感和真實感。此外，武器配件與模型本體的結合設計合理，配合飛影的高可動性，能夠擺出多種招牌戰鬥 Pose，對於作者 Fans 的小編而言，真係回憶都返曬來呀！</p><p><a title="_DSC6384" href="https://www.flickr.com/ph